      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/397/495",
      "text": [
        "۳۹۷. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): نِعْمَ الطِّيبُ الْمِسْكُ، خَفِيفٌ مَحْمِلُهُ، عَطِرٌ رِيحُهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "397. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: The best scent is musk; its weight is light while its smell is scentful."
        ]
      }
    }
